docs {
  SalesPulse project aims to create a comprehensive mobile app solution that empowers sales teams or the field forces who are involved in sales related routine tasks, with cutting-edge tools for improved efficiency and performance. This system will encompass sales order entry to invoicing, sales analytical report, daily/monthly plan or visiting entry and tracking, Point of Interest (POI) such as retailers, distributors, customers, trade partners visiting and managing their records, Geo-tracking, Geo-fencing, and day operation tracking functionalities. Entire app features and actions are maintained via offline / online syncing
  
  Objectives:
  
  - Streamline sales operations and sales order processing.
      
  - Enhance sales representative productivity and regular day activity planning.
      
  - Improve customer or client engagement and relationship management.
      
  - Provide real-time tracking and analytics for informed decision-making.
}
